%h1 Account

= form_for @user, :url => account_path do |f|
  = error_messages_for @user
  
  %p
    = f.label :name
    %br
    = f.text_field :name
  %p
    = f.label :email
    %br
    = f.text_field :email 
  
  = f.submit
  
%h2 Active Logins

- @authorizations.each do |auth|
  %p #{auth.provider.humanize}: #{auth.nickname || auth.uid}
  
Want to use another service to log into Gift List? No problem! You can add
#{link_to "Twitter",  "/auth/twitter"} or 
#{link_to "Facebook", "/auth/facebook"}.